manifest.description: A socket implementation that can run on Cloudflare Workers using native TCP connections.

scripts.test: echo e2e test in pg package

manifest.readme:
# pg-cloudflare

A socket implementation that can run on Cloudflare Workers using native TCP connections.

## install

```
npm i --save-dev pg-cloudflare
```
